data.meta_description:
8,105 likes, 158 comments - she_plusfive on February 13, 2021: "Happy early Valentine’s Day!❤️

Are you a Millennial parent?? 👉🏽🧮 What year were you born!?!? 

📼 We rent movies off Amazon Prime/ Hulu/Netflix/Disney+ instead of heading to Blockbuster.

☎️ We no longer have to memorize anyone's phone numbers.

🤳🏽 We text instead of leaving voicemails. And we dread phone calls 

📲 We can download games on our smart phones instead of playing the snake game on the Nokia. 

💿 We can make playlists instead of burning CDs.

👩🏽‍💻 We are now on the internet more than we aren't on the internet.

What else has changed for us in the last 2 decades!?!?

#millennials #millenialmom #millenialmarriage #millenialparenting #1987 #momofsix #mumofsix #motherof6 #momof6 #largefamilylife #largefamily #familygoals #valentinesday2021 #happyvalentines #felizdiadelamorylaamistad #diadelamorylaamistad #14defebrero #feb14 #amordemadre #familiareal".
